msgstr "Visa banaxelguide"


msgid "Display the center and axis during rotation"
msgstr "Visa centrum och axel under rotation"


msgid "Show Orbit Center Guide"
msgstr "Visa Orbit Center Guide"


msgid "Display the orbit center during rotation"
msgstr "Visa banans centrum under rotation"


