msgstr "Framåt/Bakåt"


msgid "Zoom by pulling the 3D Mouse cap upwards or pushing the cap downwards"
msgstr "Zooma genom att dra 3D-musens lock uppåt eller trycka locket nedåt."


msgid "Up/Down"
msgstr "Upp/Ned"


msgid "Softness"
